'''第75届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[2002年电影|2002年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]2003年3月23日下午17点30分（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚上20点30分）在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]举行，共计颁发了24座[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称[[学院奖|学院奖]]）。晚会通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]在[[美国电视|美国]]直播，由吉尔·凯茨担任[[制作人|制作人]]，路易斯·{{lang|en|J}}·霍维茨执导<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar watch: Horvitz to direct kudocast | archivedate = 2014-04-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413150506/http://variety.com/2002/film/news/oscar-watch-horvitz-to-direct-kudocast-1117876532/ | url = http://variety.com/2002/film/news/oscar-watch-horvitz-to-direct-kudocast-1117876532/ | accessdate = 2014-07-05 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2002-11-24}}</ref>。男演员[[史提夫·马丁|史提夫·马丁]]继2001年举办的[[第73届奥斯卡金像奖|第73届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]以来再度担任主持人<ref>{{cite news | last = Feiwell | first = Jill | title = Oscar taps old pal Martin | url = http://variety.com/2002/film/news/oscar-taps-old-pal-martin-1117875719/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407155016/http://variety.com/2002/film/news/oscar-taps-old-pal-martin-1117875719/ | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2002-11-07 | archivedate = 2014-04-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。三个星期前的3月1日，女演员[[凯特·哈德森|凯特·哈德森]]在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[比佛利山威尔希尔酒店|比佛利山威尔希尔酒店]]主持颁发了[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar Watch: Kate Hudson | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704143450/http://variety.com/2003/film/news/oscar-watch-kate-hudson-1117880736/ | url = http://variety.com/2003/film/news/oscar-watch-kate-hudson-1117880736/ | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2003-02-18 | archivedate = 2014-07-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥_(电影)|芝加哥]]》赢得了包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]在内的6项大奖，是这个夜晚的最大赢家<ref>{{cite news | last = Elliott | first = David | title = 'Chicago's' Best | work = U-T San Diego | publisher = MLIM Holdings | date = 2003-03-24 | url = http://legacy.utsandiego.com/news/features/20030324-9999_mz1d24oscar.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413141139/http://legacy.utsandiego.com/news/features/20030324-9999_mz1d24oscar.html | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | archivedate = 2014-04-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Rickey | first = Carrie | title = 'Chicago' wins big; Polanski surprises The musical won six awards, including best picture. "The Pianist" won three, including best director. War casts shadow on Oscars Actor Actress Supporting Actor Honorary Supporting Actress | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413142725/http://articles.philly.com/2003-03-24/news/25473316_1_supporting-actor-trophy-oscars-documentary-prize | archivedate = 2014-04-13 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | date = 2003-03-24 | url = http://articles.philly.com/2003-03-24/news/25473316_1_supporting-actor-trophy-oscars-documentary-prize | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | publisher = Philadelphia Media Network}}</ref>。其它获奖电影包括胜出三项的《[[钢琴家_(电影)|钢琴家]]》，获奖两项的《[[弗里达|弗里达]]》和《[[指环王：双塔奇兵|指环王：双塔奇兵]]》，以及胜出一项的《[[改编剧本|改编剧本]]》、《[[科伦拜校园事件_(纪录片)|科伦拜校园事件]]》（{{lang|en|''Bowling for Columbine''}}）、《[[祖布祖布斯！|祖布祖布斯！]]》、《[[8英里|8英里]]》、《[[时时刻刻|时时刻刻]]》、《[[何处是我家|何处是我家]]》、《[[毁灭之路|毁灭之路]]》、《[[千与千寻|千与千寻]]》、《[[对她说|对她说]]》、《迷人的男子》（{{lang|da|''Der Er En Yndig Mand''}}）和《双雄》（{{lang|en|''Twin Towers''}}）。晚会的电视直播平均吸引了约3300万美国观众收看，是奥斯卡颁奖晚会收视成绩最差的一次。

== 获奖和提名 ==
第75届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单于2003年2月11日由学院主席[[弗兰克·皮尔森|弗兰克·皮尔森]]和女演员[[玛丽莎·托梅|玛丽莎·托梅]]一起在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar Watch: Marisa Tomei | url = http://variety.com/2003/film/news/oscar-watch-marisa-tomei-1117880068/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407140341/http://variety.com/2003/film/news/oscar-watch-marisa-tomei-1117880068/ | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2003-02-05 | archivedate = 2014-04-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥_(电影)|芝加哥]]》以多达13项提名领跑，是历史上第8部获得这么多项奥斯卡金像奖提名的电影<ref>{{cite book | last = Osborne | first = Robert | title = 85 Years of the Oscar: The Complete History of the Academy Awards | year = 2013 | isbn = 0-7892-1142-4 | location = New York, United States | edition = | oclc = | publisher = Abbeville Publishing Group | page = 423 | postscript = .}}</ref>，《[[纽约黑帮|纽约黑帮]]》以10项紧随其后<ref>{{cite news | last = Ross | first = Bob | title = And This Year's Nominees Are... | work = The Tampa Tribune | publisher = Tampa Media Group, Inc. | date = 2003-02-12}}</ref>。

获奖者在2003年3月23日举行的颁奖典礼上宣布<ref>{{cite news|title=Nominees & Winners for the 75th Academy Awards |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/2000-2009/75nominees.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408223658/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/2000-2009/75nominees.html |accessdate=2014-07-04 |work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |publisher=AMPAS |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2014-04-08 }}</ref>。《芝加哥》成为继[[第41届奥斯卡金像奖|1968年]]的《[[雾都孤儿_(1968年电影)|雾都孤儿]]》以来首部拿下最佳影片奖的[[歌舞片|歌舞片]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Chicago celebrates at Oscars | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140315050617/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2867797.stm | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2867797.stm | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | work = BBC News | publisher = BBC | date = 2003-03-24 | archivedate = 2014-03-15}}</ref>。29岁的[[阿德里安·布罗迪|阿德里安·布罗迪]]刷新了获[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角奖]]时最年轻演员的纪录<ref>{{cite news | last = Wloszczyna | first = Susan | title = A kiss isn't just a kiss | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407084835/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/2003-03-30-adrien-brody_x.htm | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/2003-03-30-adrien-brody_x.htm | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2003-03-30 | archivedate = 2014-04-07}}</ref>。[[梅丽尔·斯特里普|梅丽尔·斯特里普]]以13项提名成为获奥斯卡金像奖提名数量最多的演员<ref>{{cite news | last = Welkos | first = Robert W. | title = The Harveys | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407123350/http://articles.latimes.com/2003/feb/12/entertainment/et-welkos12 | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2003/feb/12/entertainment/et-welkos12 | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2003-02-12 | archivedate = 2014-04-07}}</ref>。同时获男主角奖提名的[[杰克·尼科尔森|杰克·尼科尔森]]又刷新了自己创下的男演员提名数量纪录，达到12次<ref>{{cite news | last = Lyman | first = Rick | title = 'Chicago' Tops Oscar Nominees; Miramax Lifted Into Front Ranks Among Studios | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417111750/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/02/12/movies/chicago-tops-oscar-nominees-miramax-lifted-into-front-ranks-among-studios.html | archivedate = 2014-04-17 | work = Los Angeles Times | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2003/02/12/movies/chicago-tops-oscar-nominees-miramax-lifted-into-front-ranks-among-studios.html | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2003-02-12}}</ref>。[[朱丽安·摩尔|朱丽安·摩尔]]成为第9位[[一年获两项奥斯卡金像奖提名演员列表|在同一年中获得两个表演类奖项提名]]的演员<ref>{{cite news|last=Karger |first=Dave |title=Moore or Less |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,418949,00.html |accessdate=2014-07-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407071522/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C418949%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-04-07 |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Warner |date=2003-02-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[8英里|8英里]]》插曲“{{lang|en|Lose Yourself}}”成为第一首拿下[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|原创歌曲奖]]的[[嘻哈音乐|饶舌]]歌曲<ref>{{cite news | last = Vaziri | first = Aidin | title = Oscar's 9 best original song winners | archivedate = 2014-04-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081409/http://www.sfgate.com/music/article/Oscar-s-9-best-original-song-winners-3356279.php | url = http://www.sfgate.com/music/article/Oscar-s-9-best-original-song-winners-3356279.php | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-07-04 | work = The San Francisco Chronicle | publisher = Hearst Corporation | date = 2012-02-26}}</ref>。

